  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Otherworldly Concoction",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "异界混合物",
    "TraditionalChinese": "超凡混合物"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "Thick and warm, the liquid in this jar is both deeply comforting and deeply unsettling, both familiar and repulsive at the same time.<br><br>A shape forms in the surface, impossible and yet unmistakeable: <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">PR_10</span><>.<br><br>Present the elixir at a <span class=\"name name-special\">portal</span>, or consume it with <span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span> to commune with those beyond the boundaries of reality.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "罐子里的液体浓厚而温暖，让人既感到无比舒适又感到无比不安，那是一种既熟悉又令人厌恶的感觉。<br><br>液体表面形成了一个不可思议的诡异形状：<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">PR_10</span><>。<br><br>将灵药带至一处<span class=\"name name-special\">传送门</span>，或者使用<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>服下灵药以与现实边界之外的存在进行通讯......",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這個罐子裡的液體既濃稠又溫暖，既能安撫人心，卻又令人深感不安；既熟悉，又令人厭惡。<br><br>表面形成了一個形狀，難以理解，卻又清晰不已：<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">PR_10</span><>。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-special\">傳送門</span>獻上靈藥，或者使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span> 服用靈藥，與現實邊界外的異物交流。"
  },
